<fieldset style="margin-bottom: 5px;">
	<legend>Electronic Signature</legend>
	<div id="electronicSign">
		<p>I hereby acknowledge that I have been given information about the aforementioned benefit coverage.  
		By selection and signature, I authorize Great Lakes Energy to deduct the employee contribution for the 
		coverage(s) from my paycheck, where applicable.  I understand Great Lakes Energy may change the employee 
		contribution amount(s) with notice and the change will automatically show in my next paycheck provided; 
		however, if the cost change is significant I may revoke my election</p><br />
		<p>Otherwise, I understand my elections are binding and cannot be changed until the next plan year unless 
		I experience a qualifying life status change (as defined in the plan) and notify Human Resources within 30
		days of the event.  Any person who with intent to defraud or knowing that s/he is facilitating a false or 
		deceptive statement may be guilty of insurance fraud.</p><br />	
		
		<table>
			<tr>
				<td><b>Name (First MI Last):</b></td>
				<td><g:textField name="firstName" style="width: 85px;" maxlength="30" />
					<g:textField name="mi" style="width: 10px;" maxlength="1" />
					<g:textField name="lastName" style="width: 85px" maxlength="30" /></td>
				<td style="padding-left: 20px;"><b>Date of Birth:</b></td>
				<td><g:datePicker name="dateOfBirth" precision="day" /></td>
				<td style="padding-left: 20px;"><b>Employee Number:</b></td>
				<td><g:textField name="employeeNo" maxlength="5" style="width: 50px;" value="${params.employeeID}" /></td>
				<td style="padding-left: 20px;"><b>I Agree</b></td>
				<td><g:checkBox name="agree" checked="false" /></td>
			</tr>
		</table>
	</div>
</fieldset>